Text:
Thanks a lot :)

I did some research on this and it could be that the way the BT protocol is partly to blame for this:
http://thepiratebay.sx/torrent/8043682/Insex_2003_%28rm%29-------The_Chair_Day_3_RAW_%28411%29.

In short, BT can put parts of two files into the same chunk. So if someone only seeds one file, the other one can't be downloaded either.
